title: The ULTIMATE Mini ITX Case?  Streacom DA2 Review
description: The Streacom DA2 may just be the most versatile SFF mini ITX PC case we've tested.  It can fit a full PC gaming system with a a 280mm radiator. But it is quite expensive and there are some limitations you need to know about before buying it.    Learn more about the DA2 ITX case here:    Buy items in this video from Amazon at the links below:  i7-8700K:   i5-8600K:   ASUS Z370 ITX:   NZXT X62:   Lian Li Strimer:   Thermaltake Riing Trio:   Team Xcalibur Memory:   Corsair SFX 600W:   Samsung 960 PRO:    Sponsors:  TEAM Delta R 500GB SSD:   TEAM Delta R 250GB SSD:   TEAM Delta R 1TB SSD:   Corsair STRAFE mk.2:   Corsair K70 mk.2:     Subscribe    Review unit provided free of charge by Streacom.
